Package: gmusicbrowser
Architecture: all
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Depends: perl, libgtk3-perl, libgtk-3-0, libutf8-all-perl
Recommends: libintl-perl, libnet-dbus-perl, libglib-object-introspection-perl, gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0, libdigest-crc-perl, libhtml-parser-perl, libio-compress-perl, libmojolicious-perl, libtext-autoformat-perl, libxml-perl
Suggests: mpv, mplayer, mpg123, vorbis-tools, alsa-utils, gir1.2-webkit2, gir1.2-notify, gir1.2-wnck, gir1.2-poppler
Description: very customizable jukebox for large collections of music files
 The interface is extremely customizable. It has easy access to related songs
 (same artist/album/title), supports multiple genres per song, ratings, and
 customizable labels. Powerful search system, random mode and mass-tagging
 dialog. Uses GStreamer, mpg321/ogg123/flac123 or mplayer for playback. 
Homepage: http://gmusicbrowser.org/

